      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. it's a bit too generic though. could you make it sound a little less like a template? specifically, can you add a sentence or two that acknowledges how tough the decision was because their technical skills were so high? i want it to feel a bit more personal so they don't feel like just another number, but please keep the tone very professional and corporate.",
