      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Absolutely, here's a revised version:\n\n---\n\nSubject: Update on Your Job Application at [Company's Name]\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nI wanted to personally reach out to you after some thoughtful deliberation of your application for the senior developer position here at [Company's Name]. We are genuinely impressed by your technical abilities and the passion you bring to your craft. Choosing the right candidate was a difficult decision, especially given the high caliber of skills displayed in your application.\n\nAfter going through several qualified applicants, we have opted to move forward with another candidate whose experience and skills are a closer match to our intricate needs for this role. Choosing to extend an offer was never easy, but knowing your caliber, we felt it was the right decision for us Moving forward.\n\nPlease know we genuinely appreciate your interest in joining our team, and we wish you well in your job search and future professional endeavors. Your dedication and skills are evident, and we encourage you to apply again in the future.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Full Name]  \n[Your Job Title]  \n[Company's Name]  \n[Contact Information]\n\n---\n\nI hope this addition helps to make the message more personal while staying professional. Let me know if you have any more feedback!",
